{"Answer Id": 2901136, "Useful": "", "Edit Id": 161461179, "Category": NaN, "Tags": "<javascript><formatting><numbers>", "Comment Id": 32914543, "Tangled": "", "Before": [], "Confirmed": 0, "Question Id": 2901102, "Comment": "@Kerry, this `number_format('str')` returns '0'. I think it's far from interpretation.", "After": ["    function number_format(number, decimals, dec_point, thousands_sep) {
        // http://kevin.vanzonneveld.net
