{"Answer Id": 30199210, "Useful": 1, "Edit Id": 90317647, "Category": "Solution", "Tags": "<java><reflection><enums>", "Comment Id": 48504158, "Tangled": 0, "Before": ["    import java.lang.reflect.Field;
